insert  into `GLP_FAQ`(`ID`,`TITLE`,`CONTENT`,`PARENT_ID`,`I_ORDER`,`CREATOR_USER_ID`,`CREATE_DATE`,`MODIFY_DATE`,`MODIFIER_USER_ID`,`STATUS`) values (16,'1.General',NULL,NULL,1,2,'2014-05-08 10:15:41','2014-05-08 14:28:52',2,'1'),(17,'2.Global Search',NULL,NULL,2,2,'2014-05-08 10:15:54','2014-05-08 14:28:56',2,'1'),(18,'3.Points',NULL,NULL,3,2,'2014-05-08 10:16:04','2014-05-08 14:28:59',2,'1'),(19,'4.Account',NULL,NULL,4,2,'2014-05-08 10:16:13','2014-05-08 14:29:02',2,'1'),(20,'5.User Center',NULL,NULL,5,2,'2014-05-08 10:16:23','2014-05-08 14:29:04',2,'1'),(21,'6.Personal Data',NULL,NULL,6,2,'2014-05-08 10:16:33','2014-05-08 14:29:09',2,'1'),(22,'7.Business Entity',NULL,NULL,7,2,'2014-05-08 10:16:43','2014-05-08 14:29:12',2,'1'),(23,'8.Business Reference',NULL,NULL,8,2,'2014-05-08 10:16:56','2014-05-08 14:29:18',2,'1'),(24,'9.Business Chain',NULL,NULL,9,2,'2014-05-08 10:17:04','2014-05-08 14:29:21',2,'1'),(25,'10.Products / Services',NULL,NULL,10,2,'2014-05-08 10:17:19','2014-05-08 14:29:24',2,'1'),(26,'11.Orders',NULL,NULL,11,2,'2014-05-08 10:17:31','2014-05-08 14:29:27',2,'1'),(27,'12.Business Activity',NULL,NULL,12,2,'2014-05-08 10:17:43','2014-05-08 14:29:30',2,'1'),(28,'13.My Business Reputation',NULL,NULL,13,2,'2014-05-08 10:17:57','2014-05-08 14:29:34',2,'1'),(29,'14.Reviews',NULL,NULL,14,2,'2014-05-08 10:18:11','2014-05-08 14:29:36',2,'1'),(30,'1.	What is GoldenLink+?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ is aninnovative business oriented search engine and community. GoldenLink+ is designedto offer you the best experience in business searching and facilitate yourbusiness information display worldwide; moreover, it provides all the businessrelated activities inside. We provide Business search with General search,target search, as well as business activities Search. The search result will becoming up with a related industry’s business chain vision. This vision includedin two different types of categories: Products &amp; Services. <span style=\"color:red;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>',16,1,2,'2014-05-08 10:21:37','2014-05-08 14:08:04',2,'1'),(31,'2.	Do I have to pay a fee to join GoldenLink+?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ allowsyou to create an account for free. You can use all of the useful GoldenLink+tools, such as the community and the global search for free. </p><p>There are ad-on features that you may want topurchase, to make your business more noticeable to potential clients.</p>',16,2,2,'2014-05-08 10:22:01','2014-05-08 14:08:52',2,'1'),(32,'3.	What makes GoldenLink+ different?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ is aunique website that allows businesses and their potential clients a betterunderstanding of business chains.</p><p>Business owners can use GoldenLink+ to promote theirbusiness, products, and special activities that might interest clients. Theycan also connect with new suppliers / retailers and create new businessrelationships.</p><p>New businesses can use GoldenLink+ to learn about theircompetition in the area, and also to connect with other business owners, inorder to create a strong business chain.</p><p>Consumers can find information about differentbusinesses in their area, compare products and prices, and select the bestsupplier for their needs.</p>',16,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:24:56','2014-05-08 14:09:16',NULL,'1'),(33,'4.	Why should I create an account on GoldenLink+?','<p><u>Answer</u>: An account inGoldenLink+ means that your business will be seen by GoldenLink+ consumersworldwide. Your business will appear in relevant search results, which willmake it accessible to people that haven’t heard of it. It will also allow otherbusinesses to connect with you, in order to create business relationships withyou.</p><p>An account in GoldenLink+ can give your business freepublicity with no charge. The question is – why wouldn’t you open an account?</p>',16,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:25:18','2014-05-08 14:09:39',NULL,'1'),(34,'5.	Who can use GoldenLink+?','<p><u>Answer</u> – GoldenLink+ isintended for business owners – big and small, for people that plan to openbusiness, and for consumers. Each of those groups can use GoldenLink+ for theirown purposes.</p>',16,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:25:40','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(35,'1.	I am a business owner, and I want my business to appear on the GoldenLink+ search results. How do I do it?','<p><u>Answer</u>: All you should do iscreating an account on GoldenLink+ by clicking the “Sign Up” option on the topright part of the screen. After creating an account, go to “Add Business”.Define your Business entity, and you are set to go!</p>',17,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:26:05','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(36,'2.	How can I get a bigger icon to my Business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You can purchase abigger icon easily. Here are the steps:</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sign in to your GoldenLink+account</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Got to “Business Entities”</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on “Buy big Icon”</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Follow the instructions on yourpage, including the payment ones</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;After you complete thepurchasing process, your business will have a big icon</p>',17,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:26:23','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(37,'3.	What determines the location of my Business in the GoldenLink+ search results?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The location of theresult is determined by a few factors. The first is the relevancy andsimilarity to the searched term. The other factors are related to GoldenLink+search algorithm. The algorithm takes into account multiple factors, includingthe number of points the account containing the business has.</p><p>A business owner can get more points in multiple ways. Forexample, the more involved a user is in the Community module, or in rating orreferencing other businesses, the more points the account will have.&nbsp; See the “Points” section for more details.</p>',17,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:26:40','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(38,'4.	How can I change my Business’s contact information?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You should login toyour account using the “Sign in” link on the top right of the screen. Once yousee the User Center opening screen, select the first option from the left sidemenu: “Personal Data”.</p><p>There you will see the details associated with your user.You can edit and update the information as needed.</p>',17,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:26:58','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(39,'5.	What do the three options in the search mean (Product, Service, and Activity)?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ allowsyou to make a more targeted search. Therefore, if you are looking for a specificproduct, select the “Products” tab, and the search will only be for productscontaining the search term entered. This can save you time, by eliminatingresults that are not relevant for your needs.</p>',17,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:27:12','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(40,'6.	What happens if I don’t select one of the tabs in the search options?','<p><u>Answer</u>: When none of thetabs is selected, GoldenLink+ will return all the results that contain thesearched term. Those will be all the business entities, activities and productsthat contain the searched term.</p>',17,6,2,'2014-05-08 13:27:34','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(41,'7.	Although I have an account and added my business, I cannot find it in the GoldenLink+ search results. What happened?','<p><u>Answer</u>: There are a fewpossible answers. Please verify that:</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Your business address appearscorrectly, including street name, city, Country and zip code</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Your Business isn’t further onthe search result list (try browsing down the list). </p><p>If neither ofthose options solves the problem, please contact the GoldenLink+ support team.</p>',17,7,2,'2014-05-08 13:27:47','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(42,'8.	How do I use the GoldenLink+ search?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ searchis a user-friendly, easy-to-use search engine. Simply enter the search item youwant, click on “Search”, and you will receive results matching your term. Ifyou misspelled the item, GoldenLink+ will suggest alternative search items. </p><p>If you are looking for a specific entity, such as productor service, simply select the entity from the tabs above the search box. Thissearch will result in more specific result sand that can save you time.</p>',17,8,2,'2014-05-08 13:28:01','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(43,'1.	What are the points used for?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Points are used toadvance the location of your business in the GoldenLink+ search results. Thesearch results are returned according to the relevance to the searched term,and then, according to the number of points a business has.</p>',18,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:28:18','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(44,'2.	How can I gain points?','<p><u>Answer</u>: There are many waysto gain points. Here are the ways to receive points:</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Buying a big icon to yourbusiness</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Referencing a new business</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Reviewing a business, product,service or activity</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Upgrading the account to apremium account</p>',18,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:28:29','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(45,'3.	Can I redeem my points to buy a big icon?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The GoldenLink+points are not collected in order to be redeemed. They allow GoldenLink+ to seethe level of involvement you have at GoldenLink+, and to define your statusaccordingly.</p><p>Therefore, the points cannot be used to purchase a bigicon. However, purchasing a big icon is one of the actions that will result ingaining points for your account.</p>',18,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:28:42','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(46,'1.	How many users can be under the same account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Currently,GoldenLink+ supports one user under each account. </p>',19,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:28:57','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(47,'2.	How many people can use the same account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Currently,GoldenLink+ supports one user under each account. However, you can choose togive the login details to whoever you choose. Please remember that, by doing so,you are risking that your personal data and information will be available to peopleother than you. Whoever logs in into your account can see all your information.</p>',19,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:29:09','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(48,'3.	Who can open an account on GoldenLink+?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ is aplatform to support business owners new or established. Therefore, we recommendthat anyone who owns a business and wants his/her business to be known worldwide,opens an account. </p><p>However, GoldenLink+ is not limited to business owners; Itis open to anyone that has interests in businesses.</p>',19,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:29:20','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(49,'4.	Why should I open an account on GoldenLink+?','<p><u>Answer</u>: An account inGoldenLink+ means that your business will be seen by GoldenLink+ customersworldwide. Your business will appear in relevant search results, which willmake it accessible to people that haven’t heard of it. It will also allow otherbusinesses to connect with you, in order to create business relationships withyou.</p><p>An account in GoldenLink+ can give your business freepublicity with no charge. The question is – why wouldn’t you open an account?</p>',19,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:29:33','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(50,'5.	Who can see the information in my account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The information inyour GoldenLink+ account is divided into two parts: your personal information -everything found under the “Personal Data” header in the User Center, and yourbusiness information.</p><p>Your personal information, including your personal data(phone number, address, etc’) and the number of points you have, can only beseen by a person logged in into your account. Therefore, we recommend that youwill not pass your login information to any unnecessary third party, so as toprotect your privacy.</p><p>Your business information, including but not limited toyour business address, phone number, products / services, activities, can beseen by any GoldenLink+ user.</p><p>Reviews for your business can also be seen by anyGoldenLink+ user.</p>',19,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:29:52','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(51,'1.	What can I do in the User Center?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The User Center iswhere you can review, edit and add information to your account. You can addyour businesses, add products/ services related to the business, defineactivities related to your business and more. You can also add importantinformation that will make you business more attractive to other businesses orconsumers.</p><p>The User Center also allows you to reference newbusinesses, and invite them to use GoldenLink+. </p>',20,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:30:07','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(52,'2.	Who can view the information in the User Center?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The User Centeritself can only be accessed by a logged in user. Therefore, only those thathave your login details will be able to view your account’s User Center.</p><p>The information in your GoldenLink+ account that can beviewed in the User Center is separated to two: your personal information -everything found under the “Personal Data” header in the User Center, and yourbusiness information.</p>',20,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:30:19','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(53,'3.	Can I customize my User Center home page?','<p><u>Answer</u>: At this time the UserCenter Homepage is not customizable. However, the data that appears there isupdated whenever you make a change in your account. For example, every time youadd a product/service, the number of products that appear on the Homepage isupdated.</p>',20,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:30:33','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(54,'1.	I forgot my password. What can I do?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Simply click on the“forgot your password?” link next to the “Submit” button. An email will be sentto your predefined email address to allow you to reset your password.</p>',21,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:30:47','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(55,'2.	Why GoldenLink+ needs my personal information?','<p><u>Answer</u>: GoldenLink+ requestsa few basic details about you in order to be able to contact you if needed. Also,in order to avoid having SPAM information in GoldenLink+, the informationrequested from users allows GoldenLink+ to verify that there are only legitimatebusinesses in GoldenLink+.</p>',21,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:31:03','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(56,'3.	How can I view my personal data?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You should login toyour account using the “Sign in” link on the top right of the screen. Once yousee the User Center opening screen, select the first option from the left sidemenu: “Personal Data”.</p><p>There you will be able to view the details associated withyou. </p>',21,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:31:14','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(57,'4.	How can I update my personal information?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You should login toyour account using the “Sign in” link on the top right of the screen. Once yousee the User Center opening screen, select the first option from the left sidemenu: “Personal Data”.</p><p>There you will view the details associated with you. Youcan edit and update the information as needed.</p>',21,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:31:27','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(58,'1.	What is a Business Entity?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A business entity isa business. It can be a store, restaurant, freelancer business, a chain store,etc’. The business can be small or big, with branches or without. </p><p>The business you add as a business entity to yourGoldenLink+ account is the business that you want your feature businesspartners and consumers to view.</p>',22,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:31:42','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(59,'2.	How can I define a new business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: In order to define anew business entity you need to open an account on GoldenLink+. After you openan account, log in to your account, and go to “Add Business”. You will berequested to add information regarding your business. This information will bedisplayed to potential business partners and consumers in the GoldenLink+search results.</p>',22,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:31:56','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(60,'3.	Can I have more than one business entities in my account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You can havemultiple business entities under the same account. The data will be savedseparately for each business. That means that each of the business entitieswill have their own products/services, activities and reviews. The only attributethat will be shared are the points, since those are related to the account, andnot to a specific business.</p>',22,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:32:08','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(61,'4.	How can I add multiple business entities to my account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: In order to add morebusiness Entities to your account, you need to log in to your GoldenLink+account. After you logged in, go to “Add Business”. You will be requested toadd information regarding your business. This information will be displayed topotential business partners and customers in the GoldenLink+ search results.</p>',22,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:32:20','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(62,'5.	How can I view the business entities that are currently defined on my account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: In order to view thebusiness entities defined in your account l, you need to log in into yourGoldenLink+ account. After you log in, click on the “Business Entities” optionon the left hand menu. There you will view a list of all the business entitiesdefined on your account. You can also edit the details of each of the businessentities, by clicking the “Edit” link on the rightmost part of row containingthe relevant business entity.</p>',22,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:32:32','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(63,'6.	My business has multiple locations. How can I add them?','<p><u>Answer</u>: In order to add morelocations to a business, you need to log in into your GoldenLink+ account.After you log in, go to “Business Chain”. Click on the “Add Location” button.In the next screen, select the business entity related to that location. Thenfill out the needed information regarding the location. This information willbe displayed to potential business partners and customers in the GoldenLink+search results.</p>',22,6,2,'2014-05-08 13:32:44','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(64,'7.	How can I view all the business locations defined on my account?','<p><u>Answer</u>: To view the businesslocations defined in your account, log in into your GoldenLink+ account; clickon the “Business Chain” option on the left hand menu. There you will view alist of all the business locations defined on your account. You can also editthe details of each of the business locations, by clicking the “Edit” link onthe rightmost part of row containing the relevant business entity.</p>',22,7,2,'2014-05-08 13:32:57','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(65,'8.	What is the difference between a location and a Business Entity?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A business entity isthe type of business you own – what unites all the locations. For example, ifyou have a flower shop: Your business is the flower stores chain, and all thedifferent stores you have in different places will be the locations.</p><p>A business doesn’t need to have locations. </p>',22,8,2,'2014-05-08 13:33:09','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(66,'9.	How can I add information about the products/services my business provides?','<p><u>Answer</u>: After defining thebusiness entity, you can click on “Add Product/Service”, and add a product orservices supplied by your business.</p><p>We recommend you add as many products / services aspossible. That way, your business will show up on all relevant searches.</p>',22,9,2,'2014-05-08 13:33:21','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(67,'10.	I want to add my business’s logo. Where can I do it?','<p><u>Answer</u>: If you have alreadydefined your business entity:</p><p>a)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to “Business Entities”</p><p>b)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on “Edit” on the row thatspecifies the relevant business entity</p><p>c)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Add the logo in the “BusinessLogo” field</p><p>If you haven’tdefined your business entity yet:</p><p>a)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to “Add Business”</p><p>b)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Define all the details relatedto the business</p><p>c)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Add the logo in the “BusinessLogo” field</p>',22,10,2,'2014-05-08 13:33:36','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(68,'11.	I have an online business, and don’t have an address or phone number. What can I do?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Please supply thedetails you supplied when you registered your business DBA, or list your homeaddress.</p>',22,11,2,'2014-05-08 13:33:47','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(69,'12.	How can I change my business address?','<p><u>Answer</u>: In order to updatethe address, go to “Business Chain”. Select the business you with to update,and click on “Edit”. Then you will be able to update your business address.</p>',22,12,2,'2014-05-08 13:33:59','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(70,'13.	My business answers a lot of the category options in the “Business Type” section. What should I do?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You should choosethe highest category in the business type that includes everything yourbusiness has to offer. If you feel the category you selected is to general, youmight want to define your business as separate business entities, each withit’s own specialization. That way, your business will surface even in the morespecific search results.</p>',22,13,2,'2014-05-08 13:34:10','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(71,'14.	Am I required to add all the documents that appear on the “Add Business” form?','<p><u>Answer</u>: All the mandatoryfields are marked with (*). You are not required to add anything else,including the documents.</p><p>However, we highly recommend you’ll add as many documentsas you can. The more details you add, the more attractive your business will befor future business partners. In addition, you can always choose not to displaysome of the documents, by un-checking the “display” check box.</p>',22,14,2,'2014-05-08 13:34:26','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(72,'1.	What is a business reference?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A business referenceis information you give GoldenLink+ regarding a business you know or work with,that doesn’t yet appear on GoldenLink+. Both your business and the referencedbusiness benefit from the reference: The other business befits by becoming partof the GoldenLink+ database, and will now be seen by all the GoldenLink+ usersworldwide. Your business benefits, since you receive points for everyreference. The points will give you a better ranking, and will therefore appearhigher in the GoldenLink+ search results.</p>',23,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:34:42','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(73,'2.	Can I reference a business that doesn’t have a working relationship with my business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Yes, you can. Youcan reference any business you know. GoldenLink+ merely requests that youindicate if you do or don’t have business relationships with the referencedbusiness.</p>',23,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:34:53','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(74,'3.	I just referenced a business, but I didn’t see that I gained more points. Who should I contact?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The points forreferencing a new business are only given after GoldenLink+ verifies thedetails of the referenced business. Once the details are verified, and thebusiness is added to the GoldenLink+ database, the points will be added to youraccount.</p><p>If the business was added, and your account still did notreceive the points, please contact us at info@goldenlinkplus.com.</p>',23,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:35:05','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(75,'1.	What is a Business Chain?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Business Chain isthe connection between businesses. GoldenLink+ maps the connection betweenbusinesses, to allow understanding of the business market structure. This enablesbusinesses to find new business partners easily, and also to check new businesspartners according to the business mapping.</p><p>The “Business Chain” tab in the User Center enables abusiness to connect other businesses to the main business entity so as tostructure the mapping<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，</span>for example, byadding a location to an existing business entity.</p>',24,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:37:23','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(76,'2.	What is a Location?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A location is partof the business that is a unit by itself, with a role of its own. It doesn’thave to be located in a physical location that’s different than the businessentity’s location. The best way to describe a location is a business unit witha specific business role. </p><p>For example: a chain restaurant can have the headquarters,the different restaurants, and maybe a gift shop. Each of those has a separatebusiness role, and therefore each of them will be defined as a separatelocation.</p>',24,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:37:36','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(77,'3.	How are locations related to the business chain?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Locations are unitsof the business entity. Each of those units has a business role, which definesits location in the business chain. By defining the locations, a person outsidethe business can understand the business structure.</p>',24,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:39:03','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(78,'4.	One of my locations has two roles, but I’m only allowed to select one business role per location. What should I do?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Each of the location(or business units) is defined by only one role. If a location has two businessroles, you should create two locations – one for each role.</p>',24,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:39:15','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(79,'5.	Why is it mandatory to define a business role for each location?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Users might want tolearn about the location of a business in the business chain. They want to knowto which other businesses it’s related, and what is that business role in thebusiness relationship. Therefore, the role is a mandatory field.</p>',24,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:39:26','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(80,'1.	What is a Product/Service?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A product/Service iswhat your business offers to consumers/business partners. It’s the set ofoffering that the business has to offer. </p>',25,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:39:39','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(81,'2.	What is the difference between a product and a service?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A product usuallydescribes tangible items, although there could be intangible products (forexample, computer software). Service is defined as useful labor that does notproduce a tangible commodity, meaning a labor given to a consumer (for exampleconsulting).&nbsp;</p>',25,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:39:51','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(82,'3.	How can I update the details of a product/service?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Go to Products/Services,and click on the “Edit” link at the right part of the product/service row.</p>',25,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:40:04','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(83,'4.	Why should I add products to GoldenLink+? They can all be seen on my business’s website.','<p></p><p><u>Answer</u>: Some of the userswill be searching according to products. In this case, if you won’t have yourproduct defined on the GoldenLink+ platform, your business won’t necessarily beshown on the search results.</p><span style=\"font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';font-size:10.5pt;\">The products that appear on your website are veryuseful for a user that goes to your business’s website. But the trick is tobring the user to your site. Adding products to your business will cause yourbusiness to appear more often in search results, and therefore will increasethe chances of users to notice your business.</span><br />',25,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:40:53','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(84,'1.	What is an order?','<p><u>Answer</u>: An order is aservice bought from GoldenLink+. An order is created when a GoldenLink+ userpurchases one of the services that GoldenLink+ has to offer to its users.</p><p>A user can track all the orders done by his account usingthe “Orders” menu at the GoldenLink+ User Center.</p>',26,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:41:10','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(85,'2.	How can I create an order?','<p><u>Answer</u>: An order is createdautomatically every time a user purchases one of the GoldenLink+ services. Theorders relevant to an account can be viewed on the “Orders” page at the UserCenter. </p>',26,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:41:21','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(86,'3.	How can I view an order?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You can view yourorder by logging in to your GoldenLink+ account and selecting “Orders” from theleft menu. There you will also see all the orders related to your account.</p>',26,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:41:32','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(87,'4.	Can I cancel an order?','<p><u>Answer</u>: An order can becanceled, unless it is already supplied. Canceling a pending order can be doneby following this process:</p><p>a)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Log into your GoldenLink+account</p><p>b)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to “Orders”</p><p>c)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Click the “Delete” link thatappears on the rightmost part of the row containing the relevant order.</p>',26,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:41:49','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(88,'1.	What is an activity?','<p><u>Answer</u>: An activity is somekind of function related to the business entity or to one of its locations thatmight be of interests to potential customers or business partners. For example,if a business is having a special sale or seminar, and they want to invite peopleto join.</p><p>An activity can posses a market expanding related option,for example a special sale, or can simply be an event to enhance businessrelationships, like a convention.</p>',27,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:42:03','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(89,'2.	I can’t find the activity type I need on the list. What should I do?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Please use the“Other” option, and add the activity type to the description field.</p>',27,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:42:15','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(90,'3.	I want to add more than one image to my activity. How can I do it?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Currently GoldenLink+supports only one attached document to an activity. If you must add anotherimage/file, please contact our support team.</p>',27,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:42:26','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(91,'1.	What is Business Reputation?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Business reputationis the combination of reviews and rating given to a business. It is a view onlyoption for the account owner, since it is determined only by the GoldenLink+users.</p>',28,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:42:41','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(92,'2.	How can I create a business reputation?','<p><u>Answer</u>: A businessreputation is created by the GoldenLink+ users. Therefore, there isn’t anythinga business owner can do to create business reputation. The only way to create abusiness reputation, is to encourage business partners and clients to addreviews and to rate the business.</p>',28,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:42:51','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(93,'3.	Can I edit the reviews entered on my business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Business reputationis the combination of reviews and rating given to the business by its businesspartners and clients. It is a view only option for the account owner, since itis determined only by the GoldenLink+ users. Therefore, you cannot edit, deleteor manipulate any of your business reviews.</p>',28,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:43:00','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(94,'4.	Can I add a review for my business/product/service?','<p><u>Answer</u>: You should notreview your own related entities. GoldenLink+ checks all the reviews andrating, and when a business owner reviews an entity related to him, the saidreview will be removed.</p><p>However, we encourage you to add reviews for entities notrelated to you. Doing this will help your account gain points.</p>',28,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:43:12','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(95,'5.	How is the average rating calculated?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The average ratingis calculated by summing up all the valid ratings that were received, anddividing them by the total number of valid ratings.</p>',28,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:43:24','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(96,'6.	Where can users view my business/products reviews?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Whenever a userstands on a business on the map, or clicks on the business name in the searchresults, they will see the average rating, and will be able to navigate to seethe business reviews.</p>',28,6,2,'2014-05-08 13:43:35','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(97,'1.	What type of reviews can be seen in this screen? Business or product/service reviews?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The review screendisplays all the reviews the business locations received: only for the businessitself. The reviews for the products/services can be found at the “BusinessReputation” page.</p>',29,1,2,'2014-05-08 13:43:48','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(98,'2.	How can I add a review for a business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: When viewing abusiness on the map, go to the “Review” tab. There you can write and add areview to the business.</p><p>Tip: To write a review, you must be first logged into youraccount. </p>',29,2,2,'2014-05-08 13:43:58','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(99,'3.	I want to remove one of the reviews on my business. How can I do that?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Since reviews areentered by GoldenLink+ users, you cannot remove a review your business receives.If you suspect that a review is SPAM, you can contact our customer support.</p>',29,3,2,'2014-05-08 13:44:07','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(100,'4.	Who can add a review to my business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Every GoldenLink+user can add a review or rating to a business. However, before adding thereview and rating, GoldenLink+ support goes over the reviews to make sure theyare not SPAM. Only real reviews and ratings will be added.</p>',29,4,2,'2014-05-08 13:44:19','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(101,'5.	How is a review added to my business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: Every GoldenLink+user can add a review and rating to any business, when viewing a business onthe map. GoldenLink+ checks if it’s not SPAM and if it is legitimate, then thereview is added to the business, and the rating is calculated accordingly.</p>',29,5,2,'2014-05-08 13:44:32','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(102,'6.	How can I edit/delete a review I wrote?','<p><u>Answer</u>: At this point,GoldenLink+ doesn’t allow updating an existing review or rating. You can add anew review, and it will override the existing review you entered. However, youwill not receive the points again for giving a review.</p>',29,6,2,'2014-05-08 13:44:43','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(103,'7.	Can I contact the person that reviewed my Business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: No, you can’t. It isimportant that the reviews will be unbiased; therefore we do not allow businessowners to contact the reviewers. </p>',29,7,2,'2014-05-08 13:44:53','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(104,'8.	Can I comment on a review written on my business?','<p><u>Answer</u>: No, you can’t. Thereview is meant for GoldenLink+ users, to learn about your business, and alsofor business owners, to take the review to their attention.</p>',29,8,2,'2014-05-08 13:45:05','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1'),(105,'9.	What information can I receive regarding the reviewer?','<p><u>Answer</u>: The only informationyou receive regarding the reviewer is what you can see in the “Reviews” page atthe User Center – the reviewer’s name, the review, and the date of the review. </p>',29,9,2,'2014-05-08 13:45:19','2014-05-08 13:45:28',NULL,'1');
